Package org.universAAL.lddi.knx.networkdriver

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Activator  
    KnxCommunication
    Manages reader and writer for communication to the knx gateway.
    KnxNetworkDriverImp
    KnxNetworkDriverImp is the main class of this bundle.
    KnxReader
    Listens on IP network for KNX Packets.
    KnxWriter
    Envelopes KNX commands to UDP Packets and sends them on a UDP Multicast Channel.
